{"prompt": "Generate a website for a community non-profit. The website should be modern and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Community Connect</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #007bff;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.8), rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.9));\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        .section {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 40px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n        }\n        .section h2 {\n            color: #0056b3;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .section p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n        }\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #007bff;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #007bff;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Community Connect</h1>\n        <p>Building a stronger, more connected neighborhood, together.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Mission</h2>\n            <p>At Community Connect, we believe in the power of people coming together to make a difference. We are dedicated to fostering a vibrant and supportive local environment through various initiatives, events, and volunteer opportunities.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Get Involved</h2>\n            <p>There are many ways to contribute to our community. Whether you have time to volunteer, a skill to share, or a desire to support our causes, your involvement is invaluable. Explore our current projects and find out how you can make an impact.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">View Opportunities</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Latest News</h2>\n            <p>Stay updated with the latest happenings in our community. From local events to success stories, we'll keep you informed about how your support is creating positive change.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">Read More</a>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Community Connect. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}